## 사용 예제

### 예 1: JSON 읽기 및 처리

```rust
let json_str = r#"{"users":[{"name":"Kim","age":30}]}"#;
let data = json_parse(json_str)?;

match data {
    FlValue::Object(obj) => {
        if let Some(FlValue::Array(users)) = obj.get("users") {
            for user in users {
                println!("User: {:?}", user);
            }
        }
    }
    _ => {}
}
```

### 예 2: 배열 함수형 처리

```rust
let numbers = FlValue::Array(vec![
    FlValue::Int(1), FlValue::Int(2),
    FlValue::Int(3), FlValue::Int(4),
]);

// map: x → x * 2
let doubled = map(&numbers, |x| {
    match x {
        FlValue::Int(n) => FlValue::Int(n * 2),
        _ => x
    }
})?;

// filter: x > 4
let filtered = filter(&doubled, |x| {
    matches!(x, FlValue::Int(n) if n > 4)
})?;

// reduce: sum
let sum = reduce(&filtered, |acc, x| {
    match (acc, x) {
        (FlValue::Int(a), FlValue::Int(b)) => FlValue::Int(a + b),
        _ => acc
    }
}, FlValue::Int(0))?;

println!("Result: {:?}", sum);  // FlValue::Int(12)
```

### 예 3: 파일 I/O

```rust
let content = "Hello, FreeLang!";
write_file("output.txt", content)?;

let read_back = read_file("output.txt")?;
println!("{}", read_back);

let size = file_size("output.txt")?;
println!("File size: {} bytes", size);

delete_file("output.txt")?;
```

